data.value: Activity(Rate of Decay) = Decay Constant * Number of undecayed nuclei - Einstein's mass energy relation = Mass * Velocity of Light^2 - Half life of an element = 0.693 / Decay constant - Nuclear radius of an atom = (Nucleon number ^(1/3)) * 1.2E-15 - Number of atoms at end time = (Number of atom at t = 0) * Charge of an electron ^ (Decay constant * Time)
